    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Thanks for reporting. This issue has been fixed, but in order to return your database into working state, you need to do these steps:\r\n```\r\nmake integration\r\n./build/bin/integration stage_bodies --unwind 1000 --chaindata <your_datadir>/tg/chaindata\r\n```\r\nAfter that, restart your TG and it should work. If the problem persists, try to increase the unwind value to 2000, etc.\r\n",
